# AUDIO::SET_SKIP_MINIGUN_SPIN_UP_AUDIO

## Parameters
* **BOOL** setSkipSpinUp

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Set minigun audio skips the spin-up - don't forget to set this back to false after using it!
